#Slot Machine Game

This is a Python-based slot machine game that allows players to deposit money, place bets on multiple lines, and spin the slot machine. Players can win based on the combinations of symbols that appear on the lines.

##Features

- Deposit money to start the game.
- Place bets on up to 3 lines.
- Spin the slot machine to try your luck.
- Win based on symbol combinations and bet amounts.
- Interactive text-based gameplay.
- Keep track of your balance.


##How to Play

- Launch the game by running `main.py`.
- Follow on-screen instructions to deposit money, place bets, and spin the slot machine.
- Enjoy the game and try to win big!

